RuntimeSchema
public abstract class MappedSchema<T>
extends Object
implements Schema<T>

Base class for schemas that maps fields by number and name. For fast initialization, the last field number is provided in the constructor.

Author:
David Yu
Date created:
Nov 10, 2009
